  <brief_title>Evaluation of Viral Shedding Patterns and Clinical Outcomes of Influenza Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Study to Evaluate Viral Shedding Patterns and Clinical Outcomes of Hospitalized Adult Influenza Patients</official_title>
